"title": "8626: worship, places of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8626: worship, places of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Under the old covenant, there were rules governing the places where worship might be offered but under the new covenant the earthly location is of no importance.</p>\n<h2>Worship at places commemorating some act of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:7\">GEN 12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:23-Gen26:25\">GEN 26:23–26:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:1\">GEN 35:1</a></p>\n<h2>Worship at a place chosen by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:13-Deut12:14\">DEU 12:13–12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:2\">GEN 22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:23-Deut14:25\">DEU 14:23–14:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:18-1Chr21:19\">1CH 21:18–21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:15-2Chr7:16\">2CH 7:15–7:16</a></p>\n<h2>Worship in certain sacred places</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:5\">DEU 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:12\">EXO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:2\">DEU 26:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:3\">1SA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:28\">1SA 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:13\">ISA 27:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:20\">JHN 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Worship at the Tent of Meeting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8-Exod25:9\">EXO 25:8–25:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:42-Exod29:43\">EXO 29:42–29:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:10\">EXO 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:1-Lev17:5\">LEV 17:1–17:5</a></p>\n<h2>Worship at the temple in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:1\">1CH 22:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:15-2Chr7:16\">2CH 7:15–7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:27-2Chr29:30\">2CH 29:27–29:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:6\">NEH 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:8-Luke1:10\">LUK 1:8–1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:37\">LUK 2:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:27\">ACT 8:27</a></p>\n<h2>Worship in a synagogue</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:16\">LUK 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:15\">ACT 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:21\">ACT 15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:2\">ACT 17:2</a></p>\n<h2>Worship in the home</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:10\">DAN 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:6\">MAT 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">ROM 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19\">1CO 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:15\">COL 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:2\">PHM 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>The earthly location for worship is unimportant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:21-John4:24\">JHN 4:21–4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:26\">GEN 24:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:31\">GEN 47:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:15\">JDG 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:20\">JOB 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>In heaven worship is perfect</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:13\">LUK 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22\">HEB 12:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:9-Rev4:11\">REV 4:9–4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13-Rev5:14\">REV 5:13–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:12\">REV 7:9–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:4-Rev19:7\">REV 19:4–19:7</a></p>",
